      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a remarkably well-maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between daily utility and pride of ownership. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, having been regularly waxed and garage-kept; while you might find a few inevitable stone chips on the front fascia from highway commutes, the body lines remain straight and free of major blemishes. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple upholstery with only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster, consistent with careful use. All electronic systems, from the crisp infotainment display to the dual-zone climate control, function exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a rigorous maintenance schedule, including recent fluid flushes and a fresh set of high-performance tires with ample tread remaining. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are seamless, providing a confident and quiet ride. This is an honest, dependable car for a buyer who values a documented history and a vehicle that has been treated with genuine respect.",
